oai_dc:dc.dc:title: President's Message
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Jennings, Jerry
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: We are off on the adventure of a New Year and breeding season is already underway for many of us. As we look forward to the new challenges the year will provide, and, hopefully, to the many new successes that will inevitably stem from those challenges, let us see what we can also do for aviculture as an institution. Let us give back to it something as a token of the appreciation we have for the great pleasure we receive from working with our birds, be it as a hobby or profession.
